{"tid":140391,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"其實m記d 24蚊餐賣咁平有冇錢賺嫁？","createTime":"2017-03-02T07:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T08:27:21.000Z","uid":153,"like":4,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1308a74430fae4951749ea7490a66edc137f27dd","tid":140391,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"用麥樂雞做例子<br />\n以下全部用成本價計<br />\n<br />\n1. 麥樂雞當佢成本 $2 一件 <br />\n6 件加埋都 $12<br />\n<br />\n2. 可樂 出面賣都要 $6 罐<br />\n我當佢入貨價 $5好未 ???<br />\n<br />\n3. 薯條 呢個比較難預 因為佢一大包咁入貨<br />\n我當佢成本 $6 包 (中薯條咋，加大另計)<br />\n<br />\n4. 仲有茄汁呀 麥樂雞醬呀 <br />\n有時預到 d 比較小家既人又要比多幾包茄汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到預 $2<br />\n<br />\nTotal Cost = $12 + $5 + $6 + $2 <br />\n= $25&gt; $24<br />\n<br />\n仲未計埋 d 燈油火蠟 咁賣法 m 記咪蝕住黎做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咁多年黎加價都不無道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db84dfb17659e8548c4b080171a661eefa9d6cc8","tid":140391,"uid":83217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:02:26.000Z","msg":"你咁樣叫做開膠POST呀?"},{"pid":"6463b49bc98394143837544339b40c34faefe6b0","tid":140391,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T07:06:13.000Z","msg":"用麥樂雞做例子<br />\n以下全部用成本價計<br />\n<br />\n1. 麥樂雞當佢成本 $0.5 一件 <br />\n6 件加埋只係 $3<br />\n<br />\n2. 可樂 出面賣要 $6 罐<br />\n我當佢入貨價 $1<br />\n<br />\n3. 薯條 呢個比較難預 因為佢一大包咁入貨<br />\n我當佢成本 $2 包 (中薯條咋，加大另計)<br />\n<br />\n4. 仲有茄汁呀 麥樂雞醬呀 <br />\n有時預到 d 比較小家既人又要比多幾包茄汁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到預 $1<br />\n<br />\nTotal Cost = $3 + $1 + $2 + $1<br />\n= $7 &lt; $24<br />\n<br />\n計埋 d 燈油火蠟 咁賣法 m 記都賺到笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咁多年黎加價真係無道理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c16bd126094e70e09c070e52adbd40a2114dc14","tid":140391,"uid":56157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0